{"tid":273434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"因為旅行而失去份兼職機會，活該？","createTime":"2017-06-06T14:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T16:36:41.000Z","uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85667c4a594bfceeb639ffddf3397a04fe847e71","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:12:37.000Z","msg":"Yr3, 5月尾In左間必大公司兼職，真係想做。<br />\n<br />\n（第一個電話口頭己經話俾Offer, 話晏啲通知詳情。佢聽到我唔方便聽電話<br />\n<br />\n第二個電話，佢就開左全職offer, 返暑假2個半月了既全職offer, 仲想我早啲開工，不過一聽到我8月頭4日返唔到工，就話：我再度度時間先，有消息再通知你。（口吻聽落只係改Contract，我都未估到Hr想點<br />\n，因為佢只係知我9月要返學<br />\n<br />\n我隔左一個中打過去話：其實我開學都係9月中，都有啲時間走盞，Fulltime contract都可以既，但係咪中間唔可以返唔到？<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢就話：其實我地請人係想&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;Blabla頂全職同事。<br />\n<br />\n總結：我一早就講左我係申請兼職，你唔好蝦我啦，又唔講實際Offer，又要寸我頂唔到Fulltime <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd4fbc2026e312a5840d36a6d8e2b9524ed64c4","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"我想打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f471a37b83402f6aa535cfdfd5d25aec585ce4","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續腥Cv"},{"pid":"f6a04ed8c245c7ce17c25e6d6a9edade98154425","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"仲打算可以幫補下旅行"},{"pid":"ff1c66fe6f8f10e3dea6aa539f7e647f6192577a","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"大家煙腸兼職搵成點"},{"pid":"17ec44c877e0548c73388c93301b6b94f0e93ca1","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"48d05f05bd7f840f502b343742092ce07a4fe782","tid":273434,"uid":93492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:19